1. ./prepare_vfio.sh <address> <number_of_vfio_to_create> example: ./prepare_vfio.sh 0000:27:00.0 15
2. ./prepare_tx_json.sh <number_of_additional_configuration_files_to_create>
3. ./prepare_multiviewer_json.sh <number_of_senders>

Run tests:
./test_docker_launcher_rx.sh <localhost/ip> 50056
./test_docker_launcher_tx.sh localhost <number_of_containers> <localhost/ip>
./test_docker_nmos_tx-multiviewer.sh <number_of_containers> <video_type> <localhost/ip>
./test_docker_nmos_multiviewer.sh <video_type> <localhost/ip>

./controller_multiviewer.sh <number_of_receivers> <localhost/ip>